posts.post_content: Card has not been trimmed IMO, look how it fills up the gaskets of the holder.  I have viewed under a glass, this is an extremely full sized card. There is also no evidence of any type of touch up... Back is a scarce Pied 350, as most are Pied 150's.. Borders are full and snow white.. The last PSA 8 of this card sold for $27,000. Offered at $950 delivered, thanks...One time reduction, $750 delivered...**SOLD**
Good luck with the sale.  I'm flummoxed that all mighty PSA could have possibly made a mistake?  Flummoxed?
